[I] A new markup-based typesetting system that is powerful and easy to learn

[T] Typst is a new markup-based typesetting system that is designed to be as
[T] powerful as LaTeX while being much easier to learn and use.

[U] https://typst.app/

[A] typst Developers
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

